                    <p>starring George O'Brien and Janet Gaynor as the un-named Man &amp; Wife from the sticks torn asunder by the conniving Woman From The City, Murnau takes a simple premise but conjures what is consistently lauded as one of the finest movies of all time&hellip;featuring the original synchronised soundtrack</p>

